(101, 'Red Dead Redemption 2', '4', 1790, '褒貶不一', 'V001', '2019-12-05', 'Red Dead Redemption 2 這款由 Rockstar Games 製作的開放世界史詩級大作，推出以來廣受好評，成為主機遊戲世代評分最高的遊戲，如今更推出品質全面提升的 PC 版本，導入全新故事模式內容、視覺更新，以及更多。', '10_Red Dead Redemption 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(102, 'ARK: Survival Evolved', '4', 698, '極度好評', 'V002', '2017-08-27', '由虛幻4引擎打造的一款多人線上生存競技網遊，在一個超高自由度的開放世界裡，可以體驗採集、製造、打獵、收穫、建造、研究以及馴服恐龍等超多自由內容，感受酷熱白晝、冰冷夜晚的動態天氣系統以及饑餓口渴等現實中的生存挑戰，還要面對其它生存者的威脅，合作生存還是競技廝殺，由你決定！', '11_ARK_ Survival Evolved.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(103, 'The Witcher® 3: Wild Hunt', '4', 868, '壓倒性好評', 'V003', '2015-05-18', '當戰火在北方領域延燒，傑洛特將接下終其一生最重大的委託：追尋可以撼動世界的武器，預言之子的下落。', '12_The Witcher® 3_ Wild Hunt.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(104, 'Kenshi', '4', 438, '壓倒性好評', 'V004', '2018-12-06', 'A free-roaming squad based RPG. Focusing on open-ended sandbox gameplay features rather than a linear story. Be a trader, a thief, a rebel, a warlord, an adventurer, a farmer, a slave, or just food for the cannibals. Research new equipment and craft new gear.', '13_Kenshi.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(105, 'Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Complete Edition', '4', 1290, '極度好評', 'V005', '2019-10-17', 'With engaging storylines, classic turn-based battles, and tons of Digimon to collect, Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Complete Edition delivers everything fans loved about Digimon Story: Cyber Sleuth and Digimon Story: Cyber Sleuth – Hacker’s Memory.', '14_Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth_ Complete Edition.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(106, 'MOBIUS FINAL FANTASY™', '4', 150, '極度好評', 'V006', '2017-02-05', '《MOBIUS FINAL FANTASY》是以負責無數FF系列『FINAL FANTASY VII』『FINAL FANTASYXIII』的北瀨佳範為中心，與公司內部負責的開發「FINAL FANTASY」系列的夥伴們所製作的高質量RPG手機遊戲。', '106_MOBIUS FINAL FANTASY.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(107, 'Trine 4: The Nightmare Prince', '4', 438, '極度好評', 'V007', '2019-10-08', 'The best-selling Trine series returns to the magic of 2.5D! Join three iconic heroes as they set off on a quest through fantastical fairytale landscapes to save the world from the Nightmare Prince’s shadows.', '16_Trine 4_ The Nightmare Prince.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(108, 'Euro Truck Simulator 2', '4', 468, '壓倒性好評', 'V008', '2012-10-12', 'Travel across Europe as king of the road, a trucker who delivers important cargo across impressive distances! With dozens of cities to explore, your endurance, skill and speed will all be pushed to their limits.', '17_Euro Truck Simulator 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(109, 'Trove', '4', 150, '極度好評', 'V009', '2015-07-09', 'Grab your friends, hone your blades, and set off for adventure in Trove, the ultimate action MMO!', '18_Trove.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(110, '龍崖', '4', 186, '極度好評', 'V010', '2018-05-11', '龍崖是一款包含著豐富多樣的技能、物品和成長體系的半放置遊戲。玩家可以培養冒險者、打寶造裝備、配置天賦點、研究技法、提升城鎮、對外探索、解鎖卷軸，打造風格各異的強大戰隊！', '19_龍崖.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(111, 'Grand Theft Auto IV', '4', 648, '極度好評', 'V001', '2008-12-02', 'What does the American dream mean today? For Niko Bellic fresh off the boat from Europe, it is the hope he can escape from his past. For his cousin, Roman, it is the vision that together they can find fortune in Liberty City, gateway to the land of opportunity.', '20_Grand Theft Auto IV.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(112, 'Grim Dawn', '4', 588, '壓倒性好評', 'V002', '2016-02-25', 'Enter an apocalyptic fantasy world where humanity is on the brink of extinction, iron is valued above gold and trust is hard earned. This ARPG features complex character development, hundreds of unique items, crafting and quests with choice & consequence.', '21_Grim Dawn.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(113, 'Don\'t Starve Together', '4', 268, '壓倒性好評', 'V003', '2016-04-21', '《饑荒聯機版》是原生態生存遊戲《饑荒》的多人聯機獨立資料片。', '22_Don\'t Starve Together.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(114, 'Dying Light', '4', 490, '壓倒性好評', 'V004', '2015-01-26', '這款第一人稱動作生存遊戲，位於一個充滿食肉喪屍的末日後世界。穿梭於一座被神秘病毒所摧殘的城市。收集物資、打造武器並面對成群的感染者。', '114_Dying Light.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(115, 'Assassin\'s Creed® Odyssey', '4', 1620, '極度好評', 'V005', '2018-10-05', '在《Assassin\'s Creed® Odyssey》當中主宰自己的命運。 從一名流浪者蛻變成傳奇人物，踏上這趟奧德賽之旅，找出你過往的祕密並改變古希臘的命運。', '24_Assassin\'s Creed® Odyssey.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(116, '7 Days to Die', '4', 568, '極度好評', 'V006', '2013-12-13', '7 Days to Die is an open-world game that is a unique combination of first person shooter, survival horror, tower defense, and role-playing games. Play the definitive zombie survival sandbox RPG that came first. Navezgane awaits!', '25_7 Days to Die.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(117, 'Trials of Mana', '4', 1490, '一致好評', 'V007', '2020-04-24', '劃時代的日本經典電玩遊戲《聖劍傳說》系列第三部，以現代規格重製為《Trials of Mana》，從頭到尾全面以3D重新打造。', '26_Trials of Mana.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(118, 'LOVE³ -愛立方-', '4', 186, '壓倒性好評', 'V008', '2019-07-25', '窮困潦倒的成人漫畫家“綴木壹成”被奇妙的緣分所指引，先後邂逅了頗有大姊姊風範的漫畫編輯“東坊城聖”，成人漫畫界的大師同時也是青梅竹馬的“志鷹伊織”，還有熱門同人作家同時也是漫研社的學妹“天羽和花”。', '27_LOVE³ -愛立方-.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(119, 'Kingdom Come: Deliverance', '4', 438, '極度好評', 'V009', '2018-02-13', 'Kingdom Come: Deliverance is a story-driven open-world RPG that immerses you in an epic adventure in the Holy Roman Empire. Avenge your parents\' death as you battle invading forces, go on game-changing quests, and make influential choices.', '28_Kingdom Come_ Deliverance.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(120, 'Middle-earth™: Shadow of War™', '4', 1095, '極度好評', 'V010', '2017-10-09', '體驗宿敵系統塑造出來的那史詩般的開放世界。鑄造新的力量之戒，在宏偉的戰役中征服堡壘，並用你在《中土世界™：戰爭之影™》中的私人半獸人軍隊支配魔多。', '29_Middle-earth™_ Shadow of War™.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(121, 'STEINS;GATE ELITE', '4', 1390, '極度好評', 'V001', '2019-02-19', '冒瀆神明的第12個理論。 ――那是由我們親手創造的偶然產物。 位在秋葉原小型古怪發明社團「未來工具研究所」，是由主角‧岡部倫太郎這位大學生所一手創立。 其最新發明，偶然地俱備能向過去傳送郵件的功能。 但也因此刮起了世界規模等級的陰謀漩渦，充滿混沌的未來就此開幕。', '30_STEINS;GATE ELITE.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(122, 'The Elder Scrolls® Online', '4', 599, '極度好評', 'V002', '2014-04-04', 'Join over 13 million players in the award-winning online multiplayer RPG and experience limitless adventure in a persistent Elder Scrolls world. Battle, craft, steal, or explore, and combine different types of equipment and abilities to create your own style of play. No game subscription required.', '31_The Elder Scrolls® Online.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(123, 'Conan Exiles', '4', 999, '極度好評', 'V003', '2018-05-08', '一款以《王者之劍》的國度為背景的網路多人生存遊戲，如今新增坐騎和坐騎上戰鬥玩法。在單人與多人遊戲中，在開放世界沙箱中生存下來，並建造你的家園和帝國，征服敵人。', '32_Conan Exiles.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(124, 'Super Animal Royale', '4', 238, '壓倒性好評', 'V004', '2018-12-12', '免費任玩線上模式：今天就來暢玩超級免費版，並將進度同步至完整版吧！選擇你最喜歡的可愛殺手狐狸、熊貓或樹懶等動物並跳傘開始這個兇殘的 64 人大亂鬥，並以上帝視角探索這個充滿高火力兵器、巨大倉鼠球，與各種異域風情生態群落的 2D 世界吧！', '33_Super Animal Royale.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(125, 'Rust', '4', 498, '極度好評', 'V005', '2018-02-08', 'The only aim in Rust is to survive - Overcome struggles such as hunger, thirst and cold. Build a fire. Build a shelter. Kill animals. Protect yourself from other players.', '34_Rust.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(126, 'Dungeon Fighter Online', '4', 150, '褒貶不一', 'V006', '2016-08-09', 'Get ready for the ultimate brawl! Dungeon Fighter Online is a classic beat-em up 2D action game with an epic storyline and RPG elements! Choose from 14 diverse classes, and unravel ancient mysteries as you punch, slash, shoot, or summon your way to victory!', '35_Dungeon Fighter Online.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(127, 'Yakuza Kiwami 2', '4', 890, '壓倒性好評', 'V007', '2019-05-09', '在這次毫無保留的極道幫派宿命之戰中，「堂島之龍」桐生一馬必須面對野心勃勃的「關西之龍」鄉田龍司。身為系列作中深受玩家喜愛的一作，現以令人驚豔的4K畫質和解鎖幀率限制，再次重現於玩家眼前。雙龍激鬥，唯有一頭稱霸。', '36_Yakuza Kiwami 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(128, 'X-Plane 11', '4', 1090, '極度好評', 'V008', '2017-03-30', 'The future of flight simulation is now! X-Plane 11 is the detailed, realistic, and modern simulator you’ve been waiting for. Intuitive user interface, 3-D cockpits, new effects, 3-D sound, living airports and world-wide scenery.', '37_X-Plane 11.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(129, 'Divinity: Original Sin 2 - Definitive Edition', '4', 1038, '壓倒性好評', 'V009', '2017-09-14', 'The eagerly anticipated sequel to the award-winning RPG. Gather your party. Master deep, tactical combat. Join up to 3 other players - but know that only one of you will have the chance to become a God.', '38_Divinity_ Original Sin 2 - Definitive Edition.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(130, '蒼之彼方的四重奏', '4', 498, '極度好評', 'V010', '2019-09-27', '《蒼之彼方的四重奏》是日本知名美少女遊戲品牌sprite發售的超人氣作品。這款以飛行運動為主題的作品在發售前夕就已集結大量人氣，在發售後更是廣受玩家讚譽成為經典。本作在2014年萌系遊戲大賞中獲得年度排名第一名、玩家支持賞金獎以及年度大賞。是當之無愧的年度大贏家。', '39_蒼之彼方的四重奏.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(131, 'Russian Fishing 4', '4', 150, '大多好評', 'V001', '2018-06-15', 'Russian Fishing 4 is a fishing simulator with RPG elements. There is no story line and the whole process is based on the concept of an open, free to roam and free to play game.', '40_Russian Fishing 4.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(132, 'The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - Game of the Year Edition', '4', 1049, '壓倒性好評', 'V002', '2015-05-18', '當戰火在北方領域延燒，傑洛特將接下終其一生最重大的委託：追尋可以撼動世界的武器，預言之子的下落。', '132_The Witcher 3 Wild Hunt_Game of the Year Edition.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(133, '《STAR WARS 絕地：組織殞落™》', '4', 1699, '極度好評', 'V003', '2019-11-14', '一段翻轉銀河系的冒險故事，就在 Respawn Entertainment 出品的第三人稱動作冒險遊戲《星球大戰 絕地：組織殞落™》等著你。一名孤立無援的小學徒必須完成自己的訓練，學會強大的新原力技能、掌握光劍之道，同時還得隨時小心帝國的魔爪。', '42_《STAR WARS 絕地：組織殞落™》.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(134, '天命奇御 Fate Seeker', '4', 599, '極度好評', 'V004', '2018-08-07', '《天命奇御》是由甲山林娛樂開發的原創武俠單機遊戲。玩家將成為「天命之人」，肩負起江湖血、天下命。任意遊走於多條主線，挑戰懸賞解謎，結識紅顏知己、習得各派武功，每個抉擇都可能顛覆命運，創造精采多重結局。', '43_天命奇御 Fate Seeker.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(135, 'A Plague Tale: Innocence', '4', 1190, '極度好評', 'V005', '2019-05-14', '跟著年輕的艾蜜西亞與弟弟雨果展開令人揪心的旅程，', '44_A Plague Tale_ Innocence.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(136, 'Hurtworld', '4', 378, '大多好評', 'V006', '2019-12-10', 'Hurtworld係一款骨灰級嘅多人求生類第一人稱射擊遊戲 (FPS)，喺遊戲中一旦你建立咗一啲基本需求後，不斷 探索求生就變得必不可少。Hurtworld專為骨灰級玩家射擊，就係為咗淘汰對手而生存。', '45_Hurtworld.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(137, '太吾绘卷 The Scroll Of Taiwu', '4', 318, '極度好評', 'V007', '2018-09-21', '*The Scroll of Taiwu* is an indie game based on Chinese mythology and Wuxia tales. You will play as a \"successor of Taiwu\" in a fictional universe, defeating your greatest enemy under the effort and sacrifice of many generations and change the fate of humankind.', '46_太吾绘卷 The Scroll Of Taiwu.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(138, 'The Forest', '4', 318, '壓倒性好評', 'V008', '2018-04-30', 'As the lone survivor of a passenger jet crash, you find yourself in a mysterious forest battling to stay alive against a society of cannibalistic mutants. Build, explore, survive in this terrifying first person survival horror simulator.', '138_The Forest.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(139, 'Ultimate Chicken Horse', '4', 268, '壓倒性好評', 'V009', '2016-03-04', 'Ultimate Chicken Horse 是一款由玩家自行創作關卡的互動遊戲，在想方設法妨礙對手到達終點的同時，也不要栽在自己設下的陷阱和障礙面前。', '48_Ultimate Chicken Horse.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(140, '愛麗婭的明日盛典！', '4', 598, '極度好評', 'V010', '2019-11-15', '《愛麗婭的明日盛典！》是日本美少女遊戲品牌NanaWind（七風社）於2014年發售的魔法校園戀愛題材作品。本作由業界著名畫師七尾奈留及其密友Mitha首次聯袂擔當原畫與人設，並由桐谷華、秋野花等當紅聲優擔當女主角配音，是喜歡萌系人設與校園題材的美少女遊戲玩家不可錯過的一款佳作。', '49_愛麗婭的明日盛典！.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:26', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(141, 'Human: Fall Flat', '4', 398, '壓倒性好評', 'V001', '2016-07-22', 'Human: Fall Flat is a quirky open-ended physics-based puzzle platformer set in floating dreamscapes. Your goal is to find the exit of these surreal levels by solving puzzles with nothing but your wits. Local co-op for 2 players and up to 8 online for even more mayhem!', '50_Human_ Fall Flat.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(142, 'PAGUI打鬼', '4', 399, '大多好評', 'V002', '2019-10-08', '台灣早期年代，一位被宮廟收留的孤兒，無意間聽到自己的身世，於是在大半夜瞞著宮廟，踏上尋親的”奇幻之旅”。', '51_PAGUI打鬼.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(143, 'Project Winter', '4', 318, '極度好評', 'V003', '2019-05-23', 'The perfect game to back-stab your friends. Project Winter is an 8 person multiplayer game focusing on social deception and survival. Communication and teamwork is essential to the survivors’ ultimate goal of escape. Gather resources, repair structures, and brave the wilderness together.', '52_Project Winter.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(144, 'Gal*Gun 2', '4', 749, '極度好評', 'V004', '2018-07-20', '『少女☆射擊2』是一款因為奇妙事件而成為超級萬人迷的主角，使用眼力（通稱：費洛蒙射擊）讓接二連三前來追求的女孩子們升天，並以屬意的女主角為目標的奇特眼力射擊遊戲。 有點無厘頭又色色的內容依然健在！...', '53_Gal_Gun 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(145, 'Kingdom Under Fire 2', '4', 999, '大多好評', 'V005', '2019-11-18', 'Create your hero and lead your troops on the battlefields of Bersia! Kingdom Under Fire 2 is an action-packed MMORPG/RTS hybrid. Choose one of five heroes, explore a fantasy world and hone your skills until you and your troops are ready for the epic-scale battles of this colossal war!', '54_Kingdom Under Fire 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(146, 'DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2', '4', 1290, '極度好評', 'V006', '2016-10-27', '知名的DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE推出續作──DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2。 畫面表現提升後的DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2，將帶領你進入史上最龐大、最多彩的七龍珠世界。', '55_DRAGON BALL XENOVERSE 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(147, 'Remnant: From the Ashes', '4', 568, '極度好評', 'V007', '2019-08-19', 'The world has been thrown into chaos by an ancient evil from another dimension. As one of the last remnants of humanity, you must set out alone or alongside up to two other survivors to face down hordes of deadly enemies to try to carve a foothold, rebuild, and retake what was lost.', '56_Remnant_ From the Ashes.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(148, 'Danganronpa V3: Killing Harmony', '4', 1090, '極度好評', 'V008', '2017-09-25', '『槍彈辯駁』新章揭幕！ 『新槍彈辯駁V3 大家自相殘殺的新學期』簡介', '57_Danganronpa V3_ Killing Harmony.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(149, 'NARUTO SHIPPUDEN: Ultimate Ninja STORM 4', '4', 790, '極度好評', 'V009', '2016-02-04', 'The latest opus in the acclaimed STORM series is taking you on a colourful and breathtaking ride. Take advantage of the totally revamped battle system and prepare to dive into the most epic fights you’ve ever seen !', '58_NARUTO SHIPPUDEN_ Ultimate Ninja STORM 4.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(150, 'The Ditzy Demons Are in Love With Me', '4', 378, '極度好評', 'V010', '2018-10-26', 'Ren’s virginity is in danger as he is suddenly pushed into the school’s special girl\'s dormitory full of useless demons. Assigned as an assistant to watch over them, his happy and troublesome days as a teacher for these cute but incompetent demons has begun.', '59_The Ditzy Demons Are in Love With Me.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(151, 'MO:Astray', '4', 450, '壓倒性好評', 'V001', '2019-10-25', '《MO:Astray 細胞迷途》是一款像素風格的橫向動作解謎遊戲，擁有特殊能力的主角MO將藉由跳躍、黏著和各種特異能力，在怪異混沌的敵人和陷阱環伺之下，突破充滿巧思的關卡謎題設計。', '60_MO_Astray.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(152, 'Sniper Elite 4', '4', 1248, '極度好評', 'V002', '2017-02-13', '在史上最大也最先進的第二次世界大戰射擊遊戲中，盡享無與倫比的自由狙擊。在波瀾壯闊的關卡中體驗戰術級別的第三人稱戰鬥、遊戲方式選擇，以及史詩般的長距離射擊，從法西斯主義的魔掌中讓戰爭時期的義大利得到解放。', '61_Sniper Elite 4.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(153, 'Nostos', '4', 318, '褒貶不一', 'V003', '2019-12-06', 'Nostos is a cross-platform multiplayer game for PC & VR in an open world setting, where Oriental animation elements are found. You can explore with friends, discover historical sites and remains of war, build shelters and fight, uncovering the truth hidden by time and tasting the past stories of hope or regret.', '62_Nostos.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(154, 'Tools Up!', '4', 318, '大多好評', 'V004', '2019-12-03', 'Tools Up! is an exciting local co-op that tests your renovation and teamwork skills. Paint walls, tear off wallpaper, and move couches against the clock!', '63_Tools Up!.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(155, 'Eco', '4', 438, '極度好評', 'V005', '2018-02-06', 'Create a civilization capable of stopping a meteor without destroying the ecosystem in the process.', '64_Eco.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(156, 'Plane Mechanic Simulator', '4', 226, '褒貶不一', 'V006', '2019-02-13', 'Plane Mechanic Simulator讓您在英國戰役開始時擔任英國皇家空軍地勤人員的角色。 您將面臨各種任務，從簡單的加油到發動機維修和噴槍協調。 為了給您帶來最佳體驗，我們精心重建了那個時代的3架具有傳奇色彩的英國飛機.', '65_Plane Mechanic Simulator.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(157, 'FINAL FANTASY XV WINDOWS EDITION', '4', 1490, '極度好評', 'V007', '2018-03-06', '踏上冒險之旅，盡享無以倫比的高品質體驗。獻上各式各樣的豐富追加內容，支援超高解析度的畫面和 HDR 10 規格，現在你可以盡情享受精心打造、畫面唯美且前所未有的《FINAL FANTASY XV》極致體驗。', '157_FINAL FANTASY XV WINDOWS EDITION.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(158, 'Life is Feudal: MMO', '4', 150, '褒貶不一', 'V008', '2018-01-12', 'Hardcore and realistic, Life is Feudal: MMO showcases medieval life on a grand scale. Players will use survival skills, immersive RPG features, a thriving economy, community building, diplomacy and warfare to survive and flourish in the unforgiving world of Abella.', '67_Life is Feudal_ MMO.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(159, 'For The King', '4', 318, '極度好評', 'V009', '2018-04-19', 'For The King是一款結合桌遊和 roguelike 類型元素的跨越領域戰略型 RPG 遊戲。可以在線和單機進行單人或多人合作的遊戲體驗。', '68_For The King.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(160, 'Green Hell', '4', 378, '極度好評', 'V010', '2019-09-05', '《Green Hell》是悶熱的亞馬遜雨林中上演的一場求生奮鬥。掙扎求生的玩家將面臨耐力的極限挑戰，因為孤獨感不只對身體，更會對心靈構成重大考驗。', '69_Green Hell.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(161, 'Prototype 2', '4', 1237, '極度好評', 'V001', '2012-07-23', 'Become the ultimate shape-shifting weapon!', '70_Prototype 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(162, 'House Party', '4', 378, '極度好評', 'V002', '2017-06-30', '你被邀请来到了House Party！这是属于你的夜晚！你可以选择好好做人，或者做个讨人厌的混蛋！新的故事线和选择都将取决于你的选择！快啦吧，派对已经开始了，就等你出场啦！', '71_House Party.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(163, 'Strange Brigade', '4', 698, '極度好評', 'V003', '2018-08-27', '巫后賽泰吉再次捲土重來，只有一支由英勇無畏的英雄組成的部隊才有膽量與她手下的木乃伊畸形部隊抗衡。', '72_Strange Brigade.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(164, 'Hero Siege', '4', 140, '大多好評', 'V004', '2014-01-29', 'Hero Siege is a Hack N Slash Roguelike RPG with randomly generated zones, loot, randomized enemies, bosses and more! 4 Player Online Multiplayer!', '73_Hero Siege.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(165, '泡沫冬景', '4', 268, '極度好評', 'V005', '2020-01-03', '每個人都有自己的故事。片岡智的那支筆，書寫的到底是邂逅於1988的中國少年與日本少女，還是沉浮於此刻的你和我？這是中日的創作者們共同打造的奇跡，這是一款不多見的現實主義視覺小說，這是他們的故事，也是你的。', '74_泡沫冬景.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(166, 'G2 Fighter / 基因特工', '4', 278, '極度好評', 'V006', '2019-08-28', 'G2 FIGHTER is a Low Poly, third-person ARPG. Gameplay includes not only fast-paced shooting, but also role play, team fight, base construction and so many other elements. Step on unknown journey with Bern Pierron to seek for the truth of this chaos world.', '75_G2 Fighter _ 基因特工.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(167, 'MONSTER HUNTER: WORLD', '2', 1960, '極度好評', 'V007', '2018-08-09', '新的生命之地。狩獵, 就是本能! 在最新作「Monster Hunter: World」中, 玩家可以體驗終極的狩獵生活, 活用新建構的世界中各種各樣的地形 與生態環境享受狩獵的驚喜與興奮。', '1_MONSTER HUNTER_ WORLD.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(168, 'Counter-Strike: Global Offensive', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V008', '2012-08-21', '《絕對武力：全球攻勢》（CS: GO）延續了 1999 年原作在團隊競技類遊戲上取得的傲人成就。 CS: GO 包含了全新地圖、人物、武器、全新的遊戲模式，並提供了新版的 CS 經典內容（de_dust2 等地圖）。', '2_Counter-Strike_ Global Offensive.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(169, 'Warframe', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V009', '2013-03-25', 'Warframe 是一款在不斷變化的科幻世界中的多人合作免費在線動作遊戲。和你的同伴一起加入遍布太陽系的玩家與敵人對抗遊戲，駕馭 Warframe 。單獨作戰或者一起對抗威脅整個世界的敵人。', '3_Warframe.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(170, 'Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition', '2', 679, '極度好評', 'V010', '2019-11-14', '有史以來最受歡迎的戰略遊戲之一迎來 20 週年，為此我們推出了《Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition》。本作擁有驚人的 4K 超高畫質，全面重置的新原聲音樂，以及內含 3 個新戰役和 4 個新文明的全新內容：《最後的可汗》。', '4_Age of Empires II_ Definitive Edition.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(171, 'Grand Theft Auto V', '2', 990, '極度好評', 'V001', '2015-04-14', 'Grand Theft Auto V for PC offers players the option to explore the award-winning world of Los Santos and Blaine County in resolutions of up to 4k and beyond, as well as the chance to experience the game running at 60 frames per second.', '5_Grand Theft Auto V.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(172, 'PLAYERUNKNOWN\'S BATTLEGROUNDS', '2', 799, '褒貶不一', 'V002', '2017-12-21', '絕地求生(PLAYERUNKNOWN’S BATTLEGROUNDS)是大逃殺類型的遊戲，每一局遊戲將有100名玩家參與， 他們將被投放在絕地島(battlegrounds)的上空，遊戲開始跳傘時所有人都一無所有。', '6_PLAYERUNKNOWN\'S BATTLEGROUNDS.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(173, 'Tom Clancy\'s Rainbow Six® Siege', '2', 540, '極度好評', 'V003', '2015-12-01', '《湯姆克蘭西之虹彩六號：圍攻行動》是廣受好評的第一人稱射擊遊戲品牌最新系列作品，由知名開發團隊 Ubisoft 蒙特婁工作室所打造。', '7_Tom Clancy\'s Rainbow Six® Siege.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46');
INSERT INTO `items` (`itemId`, `itemName`, `itemCategoryId`, `itemPrice`, `itemGrade`, `itemDeveloperId`, `itemDate`, `itemIntro`, `itemImg`, `memberFavoriteId`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(174, 'Dead by Daylight', '2', 468, '極度好評', 'V004', '2016-06-14', '《Dead by Daylight》是一款多人（4對1）恐怖遊戲，由一名玩家扮殘暴殺手，其餘的四名玩家則扮演逃生者。逃生者試圖從殺手的魔爪下逃亡，避免被他捉住、折磨及殺死。', '8_Dead by Daylight.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(175, 'Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V005', '2017-11-16', '在《Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links》與世界各地的決鬥好手一較高下！ 進入一個時空交錯、連結所有決鬥者的世界。', '9_Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(176, 'Destiny 2', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V006', '2019-10-01', '潛入《天命2》免費玩的遊戲世界，盡情體驗反應熱烈的第一人稱射擊（FPS）戰鬥，探索在我們太陽系中的奧秘，自訂獨特的裝備給你的守護者，並釋放元素能力對抗強大的敵人。', '10_Destiny 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(177, '七龍珠Z 卡卡洛特', '2', 1390, '一致好評', 'V007', '2020-01-16', '《七龍珠Z 卡卡洛特》裡可體驗到悟空及其他Z戰士的故事！除了史詩級的對戰外，在七龍珠Z世界裡亦可以與悟空、悟飯及貝吉達等等角色進行打鬥、釣魚、用餐及訓練。', '11_七龍珠Z 卡卡洛特.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(178, 'DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V008', '2019-03-25', '光榮特庫摩的『DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation』讓玩家扮演「維納斯群島」的島主，協助『DEAD OR ALIVE』系列的女孩們在美麗與強勁的祭典—「維納斯競賽」中獲勝，並與女孩們共譜美好回憶。', '12_DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(179, '港詭實錄', '2', 238, '大多好評', 'V009', '2020-01-06', '《港詭實錄》是一款以中國香港都市傳說為題材的第一人稱恐怖冒險遊戲。故事講述一群年輕人為了錄製探靈節目“逃出靈界點”，來到九龍城寨遺址。', '13_港詭實錄.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(180, 'Hades', '2', 378, '壓倒性好評', 'V010', '2019-12-10', 'Defy the god of the dead as you hack and slash out of the Underworld in this rogue-like dungeon crawler from the creators of Bastion, Transistor, and Pyre.', '14_Hades.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(181, 'Grand Theft Auto Collection', '2', 1620, '極度好評', 'V001', '2015-04-14', 'Grand Theft Auto Collection for PC offers players the option to explore the award-winning world of Los Santos and Blaine County in resolutions of up to 4k and beyond, as well as the chance to experience the game running at 60 frames per second.', '181_Grand Theft Auto Collection.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(182, '勇者鬥惡龍 創世小玩家２ 破壞神席德與空蕩島', '2', 1790, '壓倒性好評', 'V002', '2019-12-10', '《勇者鬥惡龍創世小玩家2》一款方塊建造角色扮演遊戲。在迷人的單人戰役中進行探索、戰鬥、創造並收穫，或在可容納多達4位玩家的沙盒模式中建造大型工程。', '16_勇者鬥惡龍 創世小玩家２　破壞神席德與空蕩島.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
