(185, 'Total War: THREE KINGDOMS', '2', 1690, '極度好評', 'V005', '2019-05-23', '《Total War™: THREE KINGDOMS》是屢獲殊榮的《Total War》系列中第一款經典重現中國古代壯烈戰爭的作品。建設帝國與攻城掠地的回合制戰役，加上驚心動魄的即時戰鬥，《THREE KINGDOMS》以充滿英雄與傳奇的時代為舞台，顛覆了玩家對本系列的想像。', '19_Total War_ THREE KINGDOMS.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(186, 'Red Dead Redemption 2', '2', 1790, '褒貶不一', 'V006', '2019-12-05', 'Red Dead Redemption 2 這款由 Rockstar Games 製作的開放世界史詩級大作，推出以來廣受好評，成為主機遊戲世代評分最高的遊戲，如今更推出品質全面提升的 PC 版本，導入全新故事模式內容、視覺更新，以及更多。', '20_Red Dead Redemption 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(187, 'ARK: Survival Evolved', '2', 698, '極度好評', 'V007', '2017-08-27', '由虛幻4引擎打造的一款多人線上生存競技網遊，在一個超高自由度的開放世界裡，可以體驗採集、製造、打獵、收穫、建造、研究以及馴服恐龍等超多自由內容，感受酷熱白晝、冰冷夜晚的動態天氣系統以及饑餓口渴等現實中的生存挑戰，還要面對其它生存者的威脅，合作生存還是競技廝殺，由你決定！', '21_ARK_ Survival Evolved.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(188, 'World of Tanks Blitz', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V008', '2016-11-09', '一款緊張刺激、講求戰術的大型多人線上戰車對戰遊戲。', '22_World of Tanks Blitz.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(189, 'Black Squad', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V009', '2019-06-26', '黑色小隊是一個免費遊玩的軍事風格第一人稱射擊。玩家可以通過各種遊戲地圖，模式和武器來掌握你們的技能並展示你們的策略。', '23_Black Squad.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(190, 'Conqueror\'s Blade: Frontier (戰意)', '2', 268, '褒貶不一', 'V010', '2019-07-11', '戰意是大型的明朝背景戰術動作在線遊戲。你將一邊指揮兵團作戰，一邊陷陣斬敵，發動15V15的攻城大戰；並在歐亞地貌大世界，攻城略地，締造史詩！', '24_Conqueror\'s Blade_ Frontier (戰意).jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(191, 'The Witcher® 3: Wild Hunt', '2', 868, '壓倒性好評', 'V001', '2015-05-18', '當戰火在北方領域延燒，傑洛特將接下終其一生最重大的委託：追尋可以撼動世界的武器，預言之子的下落。', '25_The Witcher® 3_ Wild Hunt.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(192, 'Halo: The Master Chief Collection', '2', 568, '極度好評', 'V002', '2019-12-03', '一舉入手涵蓋士官長傳奇征途的六部遊戲作品！專為PC平台定制打造，本合輯內的六部力作將逐部推出。無論你是曆戰多年的硬核粉絲，還是剛剛邂逅斯巴達II戰士John-117的新玩家，《最後一戰：士官長合輯》都能給你帶來究極《最後一戰》遊戲體驗。', '26_Halo_ The Master Chief Collection.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(193, 'DJMAX RESPECT V', '2', 1360, '極度好評', 'V003', '2019-12-18', 'DJMAX RESPECT V is the latest installment from the creators of the critically acclaimed rhythm game franchise ‘DJMAX.’ Experience tracks from popular artists such as Marshmello, Porter Robinson, and Yukika, exclusive Full HD Music Videos, online multiplayer, new game modes, and more!', '27_DJMAX RESPECT V.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(194, 'MOBIUS FINAL FANTASY™', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V004', '2017-02-05', '《MOBIUS FINAL FANTASY》是以負責無數FF系列『FINAL FANTASY VII』『FINAL FANTASYXIII』的北瀨佳範為中心，與公司內部負責的開發「FINAL FANTASY」系列的夥伴們所製作的高質量RPG手機遊戲。', '194_MOBIUS FINAL FANTASY.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(195, 'Crypt of the NecroDancer', '2', 398, '壓倒性好評', 'V005', '2015-04-23', '「《Crypt of the NecroDancer》是一款獲獎的硬派節奏類Rogue遊戲。隨著音樂移動，並跟著節拍進行猛攻。', '29_Crypt of the NecroDancer.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(196, 'Trine 4: The Nightmare Prince', '2', 438, '極度好評', 'V006', '2019-10-08', 'The best-selling Trine series returns to the magic of 2.5D! Join three iconic heroes as they set off on a quest through fantastical fairytale landscapes to save the world from the Nightmare Prince’s shadows.', '30_Trine 4_ The Nightmare Prince.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(197, 'WARRIORS OROCHI 4 - 無双OROCHI３', '2', 1990, '極度好評', 'V007', '2018-10-15', '戰術動作遊戲「無雙OROCHI 蛇魔」系列最新作『無雙OROCHI 蛇魔３』終於登陸Steam®！「真·三國無雙」「戰國無雙」的眾英雄實現夢幻競演！「無雙」系列史上最多，總計170位可操控角色登場！以神話為要素的新夢幻故事（原案·監修：村山吉隆氏）！', '31_WARRIORS OROCHI 4 - 無双OROCHI３.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(198, 'Overcooked! 2', '2', 378, '極度好評', 'V008', '2018-08-07', 'Overcooked returns with a brand-new helping of chaotic cooking action! Journey back to the Onion Kingdom and assemble your team of chefs in classic couch co-op or online play for up to four players. Hold onto your aprons… it’s time to save the world again!', '32_Overcooked! 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(199, 'Warhammer: Vermintide 2', '2', 438, '極度好評', 'V009', '2018-03-08', '本作是廣受好評的遊戲《Vermintide》的續作。這款遊戲將以震撼的視覺效果和開創性的近戰動作遊戲方式，將第一人稱視角合作遊戲推向新的高度。', '33_Warhammer_ Vermintide 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(200, 'Trove', '2', 150, '極度好評', 'V010', '2015-07-09', 'Grab your friends, hone your blades, and set off for adventure in Trove, the ultimate action MMO!', '34_Trove.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(201, 'Grand Theft Auto IV', '2', 648, '極度好評', 'V001', '2008-12-02', 'What does the American dream mean today? For Niko Bellic fresh off the boat from Europe, it is the hope he can escape from his past. For his cousin, Roman, it is the vision that together they can find fortune in Liberty City, gateway to the land of opportunity.', '35_Grand Theft Auto IV.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(202, 'RESIDENT EVIL 3', '2', 1800, '一致好評', 'V002', '2020-04-03', '不管逃到哪裡也會被追至絕路。 拉昆市發生突如其來的生物災害，更為巨大的威脅被投入至這個逐漸崩潰的城鎮中…… 多重的危機、九死一生的驚險動作和重新建構的逃生劇，一一超乎你的預想。 你能逃離這片絕望嗎？ 同時收錄《Resident Evil Resistance》。', '36_RESIDENT EVIL 3.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(203, 'Grim Dawn', '2', 588, '壓倒性好評', 'V003', '2016-02-25', 'Enter an apocalyptic fantasy world where humanity is on the brink of extinction, iron is valued above gold and trust is hard earned. This ARPG features complex character development, hundreds of unique items, crafting and quests with choice & consequence.', '37_Grim Dawn.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(204, 'Dota 2', '2', 150, '大多好評', 'V004', '2013-07-09', '每一天，全球各地有數百萬玩家化身為上百位英雄，投入 Dota 戰場進行攻防保衛戰。而無論是資歷不足掛齒的新手還是有著上千小時歷練的老手，Dota 的世界都總能讓人發掘出新事物。藉由持續做出更新來確保遊戲體驗的新鮮度，Dota 2 實為一款發展不同凡響的遊戲。', '38_Dota 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(205, 'Dying Light', '2', 490, '壓倒性好評', 'V005', '2015-01-26', '這款第一人稱動作生存遊戲，位於一個充滿食肉喪屍的末日後世界。穿梭於一座被神秘病毒所摧殘的城市。收集物資、打造武器並面對成群的感染者。', '205_Dying Light.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(206, 'Assassin\'s Creed® Odyssey', '2', 1620, '極度好評', 'V006', '2018-10-05', '在《Assassin\'s Creed® Odyssey》當中主宰自己的命運。 從一名流浪者蛻變成傳奇人物，踏上這趟奧德賽之旅，找出你過往的祕密並改變古希臘的命運。', '40_Assassin\'s Creed® Odyssey.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(207, '7 Days to Die', '2', 568, '極度好評', 'V007', '2013-12-13', '7 Days to Die is an open-world game that is a unique combination of first person shooter, survival horror, tower defense, and role-playing games. Play the definitive zombie survival sandbox RPG that came first. Navezgane awaits!', '41_7 Days to Die.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(208, 'Unrailed!', '2', 278, '壓倒性好評', 'V008', '2019-09-09', '《Unrailed！》是一款多人合作遊戲，與朋友一起合作，建立一個橫跨各個程序生成世界的無盡火車軌道。', '42_Unrailed!.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(209, 'MY HERO ONE\'S JUSTICE', '2', 1490, '極度好評', 'V009', '2018-10-25', '為了各自心中的正義，戰鬥吧── 「我的英雄學院」將化為以「個性」互相交戰的對戰動作遊戲登場！ 英雄與敵人，雙方秩序誰才是贏家，命運的爭鬥即將開戰。', '43_MY HERO ONE\'S JUSTICE.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(210, 'Kingdom Come: Deliverance', '2', 438, '極度好評', 'V010', '2018-02-13', 'Kingdom Come: Deliverance is a story-driven open-world RPG that immerses you in an epic adventure in the Holy Roman Empire. Avenge your parents\' death as you battle invading forces, go on game-changing quests, and make influential choices.', '44_Kingdom Come_ Deliverance.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(211, 'Middle-earth™: Shadow of War™', '2', 1095, '極度好評', 'V001', '2017-10-09', '體驗宿敵系統塑造出來的那史詩般的開放世界。鑄造新的力量之戒，在宏偉的戰役中征服堡壘，並用你在《中土世界™：戰爭之影™》中的私人半獸人軍隊支配魔多。', '45_Middle-earth™_ Shadow of War™.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(212, 'Left 4 Dead 2', '2', 186, '壓倒性好評', 'V002', '2009-11-16', '以僵屍末日為遊戲背景：《惡靈勢力 2》（L4D2）是 2008 年獲獎無數的第一名合作遊戲《惡靈勢力》的高度期待續作。 這款恐怖的第一人稱合作射擊遊戲，將帶領您和您的朋友穿過城市、沼澤和美國南部的墓地，從沙凡那港市到紐奧良，沿途經過五章廣闊的戰役。 您將從四名全新倖存者中扮演其中的一位，並裝備一系列火力強大的經典武器與升級武器。除了槍支之外，您還有機會用不同的屠殺近戰武器幹掉感染者，例如鏈鋸、斧頭，甚至致命的平底鍋。 您將試著使用這些武器（或在對抗模式中）對付三種恐怖且令人敬畏的全新特殊感染者。您也會遭遇五種新的「不尋常」普通感染者，包括可怕的泥人。 幫助惡靈勢力呈現手忙腳亂，豐富有趣的遊戲體驗往下一代邁進，就是人工智慧導演系統 2.0。', '46_Left 4 Dead 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(213, 'Killing Floor 2', '2', 688, '極度好評', 'V003', '2016-11-18', '6-player co-op Zed-slaughtering mayhem. And now, 12-player Versus Survival mode, too - now you can BE the Zeds!', '47_Killing Floor 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(214, 'The Elder Scrolls® Online', '2', 599, '極度好評', 'V004', '2014-04-04', 'Join over 13 million players in the award-winning online multiplayer RPG and experience limitless adventure in a persistent Elder Scrolls world. Battle, craft, steal, or explore, and combine different types of equipment and abilities to create your own style of play. No game subscription required.', '48_The Elder Scrolls® Online.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(215, 'JUMP FORCE', '2', 1490, '極度好評', 'V005', '2019-02-14', '創造屬於你的虛擬化身，在遊戲原創劇情模式中與最強大的漫畫英雄並肩作戰，或是前去連線大廳挑戰其他玩家，並且發掘各種玩法。', '49_JUMP FORCE.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(216, 'Conan Exiles', '2', 999, '極度好評', 'V006', '2018-05-08', '一款以《王者之劍》的國度為背景的網路多人生存遊戲，如今新增坐騎和坐騎上戰鬥玩法。在單人與多人遊戲中，在開放世界沙箱中生存下來，並建造你的家園和帝國，征服敵人。', '50_Conan Exiles.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(217, 'DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation', '5', 150, '極度好評', 'V007', '2019-03-25', '光榮特庫摩的『DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation』讓玩家扮演「維納斯群島」的島主，協助『DEAD OR ALIVE』系列的女孩們在美麗與強勁的祭典—「維納斯競賽」中獲勝，並與女孩們共譜美好回憶。', '1_DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(218, 'NBA 2K20', '5', 1790, '褒貶不一', 'V008', '2019-09-05', '2K continues to redefine what’s possible in sports gaming with NBA 2K20, featuring best in class graphics & gameplay, ground breaking game modes, and unparalleled player control and customization.', '2_NBA 2K20.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(219, 'DJMAX RESPECT V', '5', 1360, '極度好評', 'V009', '2019-12-18', 'DJMAX RESPECT V is the latest installment from the creators of the critically acclaimed rhythm game franchise ‘DJMAX.’ Experience tracks from popular artists such as Marshmello, Porter Robinson, and Yukika, exclusive Full HD Music Videos, online multiplayer, new game modes, and more!', '3_DJMAX RESPECT V.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(220, 'Assetto Corsa Competizione', '5', 598, '極度好評', 'V010', '2019-05-29', 'Assetto Corsa Competizione is the new official Blancpain GT Series videogame. Thanks to the extraordinary quality of simulation, the game will allow you to experience the real atmosphere of the FIA ​​GT3 homologated championship, competing against official drivers, teams, cars and circuits.', '4_Assetto Corsa Competizione.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(221, 'Beat Saber', '5', 438, '壓倒性好評', 'V001', '2019-05-21', 'Beat Saber is a VR rhythm game where you slash the beats of adrenaline-pumping music as they fly towards you, surrounded by a futuristic world.', '5_Beat Saber.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(222, 'Russian Fishing 4', '5', 150, '大多好評', 'V002', '2018-06-15', 'Russian Fishing 4 is a fishing simulator with RPG elements. There is no story line and the whole process is based on the concept of an open, free to roam and free to play game.', '6_Russian Fishing 4.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(223, 'NBA 2K Playgrounds 2', '5', 990, '大多好評', 'V003', '2018-10-15', '《NBA 2K 熱血街球場2》帶著酣暢淋漓的 NBA 街機體驗再次歸來！選好你的球隊，加入街頭亂鬥，揮灑無限籃球可能！', '223_NBA 2K Playgrounds 2.jpg', '[26]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 18:24:28'),
(224, 'rFactor 2', '5', 468, '極度好評', 'V004', '2013-03-28', 'rFactor 2 is a realistic, easily extendable racing simulation that offers the latest in vehicle and race customization, great graphics, outstanding multiplayer and the height of racing realism. It features mixed class road racing with ultra realistic dynamics, an immersive sound environment and stunning graphics.', '8_rFactor 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(225, '動物之鬪', '5', 168, '極度好評', 'V005', '2019-12-18', '簡單操作x詼諧動物 X 刺激對戰!!! 選擇你喜歡的趣味動物來一場充滿野性的激烈♂ 對戰吧！你可以在遊戲中與全世界的玩家好手對戰，也能在街機模式中擊敗所有敵人，成為動物之王。本作僅需四個按鈕操縱，並且採用一鍵出招系統，沒有複雜的操作，打起來輕鬆有趣！...', '9_動物之鬪.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(226, 'Assetto Corsa', '5', 318, '極度好評', 'V006', '2014-12-19', 'Assetto Corsa v1.16 introduces the new \"Laguna Seca\" laser-scanned track, 7 new cars among which the eagerly awaited Alfa Romeo Giulia Quadrifoglio! Check the changelog for further info!', '10_Assetto Corsa.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(227, 'Football Manager 2020', '5', 1038, '大多好評', 'V007', '2019-11-18', '善用自己的想法，讓球會按你的意思而動。FM20 中每個決定都有重大影響，新的功能與更加精細入微的遊戲機制，使足球管理更真實、新鮮和富有深度，讓領隊對自己和球隊的未來肩負更大的責任。', '11_Football Manager 2020.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(228, 'F1® 2019', '5', 858, '極度好評', 'V008', '2019-06-27', 'F1® 2019官方電玩遊戲，挑戰你加入Codemasters史上最野心勃勃的F1®遊戲，極速狂飆，擊敗對手。當季所有官方隊伍、車手與21座賽車場在F1® 2019中齊聚一堂。今年更將迎來F2™，玩家可在2018賽季中一較高下。', '12_F1® 2019.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(229, 'Ride 2', '5', 568, '極度好評', 'V009', '2016-10-07', 'The fastest and most iconic bikes in the world\'s biggest digital garage!', '13_Ride 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(230, 'Liftoff: FPV Drone Racing', '5', 468, '壓倒性好評', 'V010', '2018-09-13', 'FPV Drone Racing game Liftoff! Liftoff is a game that translates the rush of first-person view drone racing to the digital world. Join the biggest community for virtual FPV racing!', '14_Liftoff_ FPV Drone Racing.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(231, 'Sonic & All-Stars Racing Transformed Collection', '5', 468, '極度好評', 'V001', '2010-02-23', 'Compete across land, water and air in incredible transforming vehicles that change from cars to boats to planes mid-race.', '15_Sonic & All-Stars Racing Transformed Collection.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 20:31:28'),
(232, 'Creed: Rise to Glory™', '5', 438, '極度好評', 'V002', '2018-09-25', 'You are Adonis Creed, fighting toe-to-toe with the world’s top opponents to establish your boxing legacy. This intense cinematic experience features new Phantom Melee Technology for impactful VR melee combat so you can train, fight, and win like Creed.', '16_Creed_ Rise to Glory™.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(233, 'Super Mega Baseball 2', '5', 318, '極度好評', 'V003', '2018-04-30', 'The critically acclaimed Super Mega Baseball series is back with new visuals, deep team and league customization, and online multiplayer modes.', '17_Super Mega Baseball 2.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(234, 'VRC PRO', '5', 958, '極度好評', 'V004', '2015-03-24', 'VRC Pro takes you deep into the world of cutting edge, modern RC cars. You can race up to 15 different RC cars on real existing mini race tracks all around the world; all fully customizable & tunable.', '18_VRC PRO.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(235, 'OhShape', '5', 268, '極度好評', 'V005', '2019-12-13', 'OhShape is a rhythm VR game where players have to move their full body to go through, punch or dodge walls following the beat of the music. It\'s an immersive game for all type of players inspired by the Japanese TV show Hole in the Wall.', '19_OhShape.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(236, 'Drone Racer', '5', 248, '2 篇使用者評論', 'V006', '2019-12-23', '想在家享受FPV無人機賽車嗎？飛過寬闊的地圖。 開關FPV與冠捷隨時查看，支持PC和VR發揮。', '20_Drone Racer.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(237, 'NBA 2K19', '5', 1790, '褒貶不一', 'V007', '2018-09-10', '替運動遊戲重下定義的《NBA 2K》即將踏入第20個年頭。一路走來，《NBA 2K》不僅提供最為出色的畫面與遊戲表現，也帶來各種創新的遊戲模式，以及足可亂真的開放世界「街區」。《NBA 2K19》將持續挑戰遊戲設計的極限，務求讓玩家獲得更接近現實的精彩籃球體驗與街頭文化。', '21_NBA 2K19.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(238, 'Ultimate Fishing Simulator VR', '5', 438, '極度好評', 'V008', '2019-11-15', 'Bored of waiting for a bite? Would you like to catch some fish? You\'re lucky - in Ultimate Fishing Simulator, fish bite like crazy! Spinning, float fishing, ground fishing and more! Now you can feel it on your own by playing it on VR!', '22_Ultimate Fishing Simulator VR.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(239, 'Rocket League®', '5', 468, '極度好評', 'V009', '2015-07-07', 'Rocket League is a high-powered hybrid of arcade-style soccer and vehicular mayhem with easy-to-understand controls and fluid, physics-driven competition. Rocket League includes casual and competitive Online Matches, a fully-featured offline Season Mode, special “Mutators” that let you change the rules entirely, hockey and...', '23_Rocket League®.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(240, 'Gym Simulator', '5', 45, '褒貶不一', 'V010', '2018-11-17', 'Extremely realistic first person Gym RPG', '24_Gym Simulator.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(241, 'Wild Animal Racing', '5', 120, '極度好評', 'V001', '2016-03-07', '野生動物賽車是一個令人興奮的卡丁車模擬遊戲與扭曲。 扮演大象，獅子，斑馬，長頸鹿，犀牛或河馬！ 玩其他動物或對一個朋友在同一台電腦上的分屏模式！ 或邀請Steam朋友在多人模式！ 在埃及，巴黎和荷蘭在世界巡迴賽軌道賽車！ 解鎖動畫，找出動物魔法力量的秘密...', '25_Wild Animal Racing.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(242, 'Fishing Planet', '5', 150, '極度好評', 'V002', '2015-08-11', 'Fishing Planet是一個獨特和高度現實的在線第一人稱多人釣魚模擬器，由狂熱的釣魚愛好者釣魚給你帶來實際釣魚充分刺激開發！ ！選擇你的誘餌，使你的戰利品，享受新的功能，並與您的朋友一起隨時隨地加強你的真正的釣魚技巧！ 遊戲是免費的，只需下載就可以了！', '26_Fishing Planet.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-25 14:06:42'),
(243, 'Pool Nation', '5', 138, '極度好評', 'V003', '2013-10-18', 'Play POOL NATION and become mesmerised by our balls, entranced by our decals & unashamedly attached to our cues, so join us please, & just have fun playing pool!! WARNING: contains addictive content!! Pool Nation, with WORKSHOP integration AVAILABLE NOW in our Crazy Mode the Box Of Tricks (Out Now)!', '27_Pool Nation.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(244, 'City Climber', '5', 138, '大多好評', 'V004', '2017-02-24', 'City Climber is a silly physics-based game about a floppy ragdoll climber, who has to save the world. Find your way through diverse hand-crafted environments and enjoy funny challenges full of falling and destruction.', '28_City Climber.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46'),
(245, 'Mountain Taxi Driver', '5', 39, '7 篇使用者評論', 'V005', '2019-09-13', '這款全新的遊戲讓出租車駕駛變得更加刺激和冒險。 作為出租車司機，找到並接載乘客，開車經過危險而陡峭的山路地形，並準時將乘客安全地送往目的地。', '29_Mountain Taxi Driver.jpg', '[]', '2020-01-16 21:13:27', '2020-03-23 17:17:46');
